      "sec_scoring_title": "Scoring",
      "scoring_0121601": "Step 1: Coding ResponsesFor items followed by [F]-i.e., items 2, 4, 10, 11, 16, 21, 25, 30, 33, 35, 39, 41, 44, 47, 50, 52, 57-code responses as follows: True = 0; Somewhat true = 1; Somewhat false = 2; False = 3.Code responses for all other items as follows: True = 3; Somewhat true = 2; Somewhat false = 1; False = 0.Step 2: Computing Scale Scores and Total ScoresBoldness subscale (19 items)-Sum coded responses for the following items:1, 4, 7, 10, 13, 16, 19, 22, 25, 28, 32, 35, 38, 41, 44, 47, 50, 54, 57Meanness subscale (19 items)-Sum coded responses for the following items:2, 6, 8, 11, 14, 17, 20, 23, 26, 29, 33, 36, 39, 40, 42, 45, 48, 52, 55Disinhibition subscale (20 items)-Sum coded responses for the following items:3, 5, 9, 12, 15, 18, 21, 24, 27, 30, 31, 34, 37, 43, 46, 49, 51, 53, 56, 58Total Psychopathy score-Sum scores across the three subscales."
